    "In all datasets, our model performs noticeably better than current models, demonstrating the efficacy of our method: text-to-text creation using the TANL framework.",
    "Our model's simplicity gives our approach a competitive edge over earlier approaches.",
    "For subtasks like span identification, component classification, and relation classification, earlier approaches had separate hyperparameters.",
